=Description=

"Habibi.Works is an intercultural maker space and platform for education, empowerment and encounters for refugees and Greek locals in the North of Greece.

The team works work at eye level with people, supporting them to create solutions themselves. They listen to their ideas instead of telling them what to do. The team encourages the community to share their skills and expertise. Habibi.Works is a living example of the values we would like to see in our societies: respect, solidarity, and equality."

